race.description: Rock At The Races 21 March @ Gosford Hcp (Bm64)
race.comment: GAMBLER (7) started favourite and looked to have every chance but missed the placings last start over this distance at Kembla. Snowden has opted to put a nose roll on which might have a positive effect. Certainly deserves another chance. BIANCA MIA (12) has not appeared since coming from the clouds to win by a whisker on debut over this course and distance four months ago. Two recent trials should have her ready to run well in this tougher contest. IRON HAT (15) is back after a four-month absence. Capable of bobbing up when fresh. Lands a top three spot at around 50% of his runs over this distance. Nice each-way option. APOLLO RIDGE (5) led all the way to collect an overdue maiden win over 1100m at Hawkesbury recently. Won't mind coming back in trip so another bold run looks on the cards. INAZUMA BOY (3) impressed last start when first-up from a long break at Scone. One to watch for late in proceedings.
